OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloudy
OL,6,Ftonight across Scotland with patchy
OL,7,Frain, heavy at times in the north.
OL,8,FElsewhere, mostly dry with variable
OL,9,Famounts of cloud, though the odd
OL,10,Fshower possible. Chilly in the
OL,11,Fcountryside with mist and fog patches
OL,12,Fin the west.
OL,13,
OL,14,CMonday:FCloudier for most on Monday
OL,15,Fwith the best of the sunshine in the
OL,16,Ffar south. Showers in Scotland,
OL,17,Fsinking southwards throughout the day,
OL,18,Fturning heavy and thundery into the
OL,19,Fafternoon.
